A Day to remember 🥺🧿♥️ #dazzlingsimranvlogs 

🏆Invited as a Guest of Honour In ARSD college, Delhi University 

Thought to show you all how was the experience like ….😍

Deets:
Dress from @laglitsbychhavi { Buy from My Store🛍️🛒 Link in bio👆🏻Code- GETHYPD}
Earings from @jewelin.in 
Heels from @urbane_shoes

#followyourdreams ♥️🧿✨

✨Kabhi kisse cheez ko shiddat se chaho toh puri kainat Apko usse milane mein lag jaati hai ✨

🎙️Special Thanks to Bharati college , Delhi university & Student who were constantly in touch with me over a telephonic conversation! 

Never thought jiss college mein kabhi mein apna admission lenne gai thi 😅usse college mein I would be invited to share my journey ,experience & motivate our young blood. Voh alag baat hai ki admission milla nahi tha kyunki tabh cut off bhot high thi🙈Bhot maza aaya baatein karke ( coz I love talking ) & trust me I needed to motivate them all kyunki kabhi uss row mein , mein khud bhi bethi thi♥️ 

Shot by 📷 : @ogmentry 

Cheers to Women ✨

#womenempowerment

🥺♥️Gurugram Meet & Greet Ft @rubys.organics 💛💚

📸Shot by - @tasveershalaaa

On 4th June ,last Sunday we hosted a meet & greet in Gurugram .The Galleries 32 Avenue in Ruby’s Organics first Store 🥰 

Thankyou so very much  to each one of you who supported through their visit by taking out time on SUNDAY . I can totally understand everyone feels like chilling on Sundays but still you all came means a lot. Really feels emotional & grateful 💖

Those of you , who couldn’t visit will meet next time for sure 👌🏻
